article_title: Free health fairs designed to reach Latinos

article_metadata.description: STOCKTON — Salud Outreach is organizing two upcoming free health fairs targeting the region’s large Latino community.The health fairs will be held from 10 a.m. to 2 p.m. Jan. 24 and March 21 during The Market at Delta College in Parking Lot B3 of San Joaquin Delta College, 5151 Pacific Ave., Stockton.Salud Outreach is a cooperative effort of several groups at the University of the Pacific Thomas J.
